  "general_provisions": "This resolution amends the Utah Rules of Civil Procedure. ",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This resolution:<hr><ltbullet>amends Utah Rules of Civil Procedure, Rule 42, to address separate trials in a medical malpractice action and transfer to a district court panel; <hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes; and<hr><ltbullet>includes a coordination clause with S.J.R. 5, Joint Resolution Amending the Utah Rules of Civil Procedure, to address the coordination clause in S.J.R. 5.",
